8.1Triggers

         Create Trigger for Drop-Off Point

            a. Trigger Name: DropOffTrigger
                Object: Drop-Off Point

             b. Click on Submit

 Description
 Creating the DropOffTrigger for the Drop-Off Point object allows for automated actions in response to specific events, enhancing workflow efficiency and ensuring data integrity within your Salesforce application.

 Purpose
 This trigger ensures that the distance between the Drop-Off Point and a related Venue is automatically  calculated and stored in the Distance field whenever a new record is created. This automation enhances data accuracy and reduces manual entry errors
